<h4 id=3D"MonitoringinwestpacMesh-WhatisSplunk?">What is Splunk?</h4>
<p><strong>Splunk</strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);"><span>&nbsp=
;</span>is a software platform widely used for monitoring, searching, analy=
sing and visualizing the machine-generated data.</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded=
-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-emb=
