<h3 id=3D"MonitoringinwestpacMesh-HowSplunkDataisbeingingested?">How Splunk=
 Data is being ingested ?</h3>
<p>in HPASS, Splunk Universal Forwarder is installed in all&nbsp;<span styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);">Westpac Mesh</span>&nbsp;servers and read the u=
seful data and send it to Splunk Cloud managed by Log insights Platform ( L=
IP ). This Data will be parsed while ingesting and stored in a Index dedica=
ted for <span style=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);">Westpac Mesh</span>. User wil=
l be able to run the searches in the Splunk Search head component's web int=
erface (&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://wbc.splunkcloud.com/en-GB/app/a008e0/" cla=
ss=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://wbc.splunkcloud.com/en-GB/app=
/a008e0/</a>)</p>
<p>In Mesh, We are pushing logs to splunk from Azure using HTTP Event colle=
ctor.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><br></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-w=
rapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-i=
mage" draggable=3D"false" height=3D"230" src=3D"f5a89b7228753b5386e5731666b=
