<h3 id=3D"MonitoringinwestpacMesh-HowtoSearchwestpacMeshDatainSplunk:">How =
to Search westpac Mesh Data in Splunk:</h3>
<p>Launch Splunk URL : <a href=3D"https://wbc.splunkcloud.com/en-GB/app/a00=
8e0/search" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://wbc.splunkclou=
d.com/en-GB/app/a008e0/search</a></p>
<p>Choose <span style=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);">Westpac Mesh&nbsp;</span>pr=
od and Non-Prod app based on what you need to use.</p>
