<h3 id=3D"MonitoringinwestpacMesh-WestpacMeshProdSourcetypes:">Westpac Mesh=
 Prod Sourcetypes:</h3>
<p>Logs which are being ingested to <span style=3D"color: rgb(34,34,34);">W=
estpac Mesh&nbsp;</span>index are categorised into multiple sourcetypes bas=
ed on the content of the log files.</p>
<p>keying these sourcetype will filter accurate results with less search ti=
me. It is important to understand what each of this source type belongs to =
while troubleshooting your logs.</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,255);">Index=3Dprd_a008e0 sourcetype=3D&lt=
;type source type&gt;</span></p>
