efault, the most recent event is listed first. In each event, the matching =
search terms are highlighted. To change the event view, use the<span>&nbsp;=
</span><strong>List</strong>,<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Format</strong>, an=
d<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Per Page</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>options.</t=
d>
