<p>Inspect search Job :</p>
<p>Using job inspector, you can examine the inner workings of a search. It =
is an excellent troubleshooting tool to diagnose poorly performing searches=
. You can compare job inspector to a relational database platform=E2=80=99s=
 SQL explain plan, which shows the<br>
 execution costs of various fragments of the query. You can invoke the job =
inspector either while the search is running or after it is completed</p>
