lass=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://conf.splunk.com/files/2016/=
slides/power-of-spl.pdf</a></p>
<p>Below Youtube channel playlist provides detailed splunk training for a p=
ower user level, highlighted related courses. U<u>se your personal devices =
to for this learning.</u></p>
